data.name: ForceNewPage
desc: Specifies if the section will be printed on a separate page.
This does not apply to page header or page footer.

items.name: NONE
lines: The current section is printed on the current page.

items.name: BEFORE_SECTION
lines: The current section is printed at the top of a new page.

items.name: AFTER_SECTION
lines: The next section following the current section is printed at the top of a new page.

items.name: BEFORE_AFTER_SECTION
lines: The current section is printed at the top of a new page as well as the next section.
